      <title>意大利总理梅洛尼表示将在未来几周访问中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/italy-s-pm-meloni-says-will-travel-to-china-in-coming-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利决定退出与北京的一项有争议的投资协定后，乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 计划在未来几周访问中国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/italy-s-pm-meloni-says-will-travel-to-china-in-coming-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 13:34:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
