    <item>
      <title>税收疑虑将困扰凯尔·斯塔默大选及以后的竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/tax-doubts-look-set-to-dog-keir-starmer-to-election-and-beyond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离英国大选仅剩不到三周，基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 的执政之路似乎已无悬念，但对于投资者、经济学家和将选举他的普通英国人来说，这位工党领袖仍需解决一个关键问题：他的税收和支出计划是否合理？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/tax-doubts-look-set-to-dog-keir-starmer-to-election-and-beyond</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
